    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You are descended from the elemental outsiders known as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/outsiders/salamander\">salamanders</a>. You wield flame as a weapon and a tool, and your smithing skills are unrivaled.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/acrobatics\">Acrobatics</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.cvv6oimqks9n62vy]{Magic Weapon}&nbsp;(3rd),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.6h3p3zr2hbrjea8k]{Molten Orb}&nbsp;(5th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.73han2zqxg59u18g]{Magic Vestment}&nbsp;(7th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.nfm6i9z9r3n2fku7]{Fire Shield}&nbsp;(warm shield) (9th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.d3a93wcwatqhywqy]{Fire Snake}&nbsp;(11th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.hzkaqaa8n6ygwmub]{Tar Pool}&nbsp;(13th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.hfca2lb4tlmrzoxm]{Firebrand}&nbsp;(15th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.h17ad4lpmphnospf]{Wall of Lava}&nbsp;(17th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.xhzme0v6tjq95fg6]{Meteor Swarm}&nbsp;(19th).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Zeq6RWYv5otvg8q7]{Cleave},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.tD76K8QGco9scT0r]{Craft Wondrous Item},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.iAbIGhm7T2OK9Brt]{Iron Will},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.FUW5mIXHNBBIQ1Sq]{Power Attack},&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/general-feats/prodigy\">Prodigy</a>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/acrobatics\">Acrobatics</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.8snLqsJN4LLL00Nq]{Toughness}.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> The DCs of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;spells increase by 2 against creatures that are suffering ongoing fire damage.</p>",
